# {{ project_name }} - JupyterHub Deployment

Local deployment overlay of [stellars-jupyterhub-ds](https://github.com/stellarshenson/stellars-jupyterhub-ds), generated from the [deployment template](https://github.com/stellarshenson/copier-stellars-jupyterhub-ds).

## Overview

- Multi-user JupyterHub 4 platform with GPU support and NativeAuthenticator
- {{ project_name }} branding (logo, JupyterLab top-bar icon, browser favicon)
- Bundled local reverse proxy ([Traefik](https://traefik.io/)) with self-signed TLS certificates

